com.credenceid.database

Class BiometricData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.credenceid.database.BiometricData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FaceRecord, FingerprintRecord, IrisRecord

    public class BiometricData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing generic biometric data type. This is a parent class to following classes.
    • FingerprintRecord
    • FaceRecord
    • IrisRecord

    This class stores generic image and template data for a biometric. Each child class is responsible for storing it's biometric types specific data.
